            <p>The hero dimensions are set to hero fixed height, as outlined in the photography section of this guide. We recommend using only two image ratios for desktop, large or small, to best accommodate all screen types. The hero image also goes full-bleed no matter the viewport size, so exporting assets to the largest image size possible is recommended.</p>

            <h5 class="font-weight-bold mt-5 mb-2">Desktop Hero Large </h5>
